Package: trajclass
Title: Classification of Longitudinal Trajectories / Time Series
Version: 0.0.0.9008
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for preparing and classifying longitudinal trajectories 
    (time series) into shape-based categories such as linear, quadratic, 
    and hockey-stick (segmented with one breakpoint).
